A novel PAX6 deletion in a Chinese family with congenital aniridia.

Liu Q(1), Wan W(2), Liu Y(1), Liu Y(2), Hu Z(1), Guo H(1), Xia K(3), Jin X(4).

Author information:
(1)State Key Laboratory of Medical Genetics, Central South University, Changsha, 
Hunan, China.
(2)The First Affiliated Hospital of Zhengzhou University, Zhengzhou, Henan, 
China.
(3)State Key Laboratory of Medical Genetics, Central South University, Changsha, 
